{"tid":1746941,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[筍工] 清潔工日薪$200萬元","createTime":"2019-11-23T03:46:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-23T03:46:28.000Z","uid":42188,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"0f8915ea3618b07d3107ccd09cf0a103f907cabf","tid":1746941,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T03:46:28.000Z","msg":"陸媒澎湃新聞以及中共旗下香港大公傳媒集團近日聯合為兩名因「反送中」運動而傷亡者募款，並在8小時內達到籌款人民幣200萬元（約合新台幣860萬元）的目標。<br />\n<br />\n據澎湃新聞，截至昨天深夜11時許，<span style=\"color: red;\">這個名為「香港李伯羅伯專項救助基金」項目在8小時內達到籌款200萬元的目標</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢個仔有首期去買樓啦"}]}